title: Trade Deadline Recap  | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin is joined Yahoo Sports senior NFL reporter Charles Robinson to discuss why guys like Will Fuller of the Houston Texans and Stephon Gilmore of the New England Patriots didn’t get moved (2:40). Then they discuss how the Patriots (15:30) and Cowboys can look to improve (23:05).
Host: Kevin Clark
Guest: Charles Robinson
